      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022 R2 used under ISO 9001-certified QMS; regression test suite covers 142 benchmark cases; version-controlled simulation scripts stored in institutional GitLab repository with tagged releases."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
