    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels with the exception of Discretization Error, which achieved Gradation 1 against a required Gradation 2. The assessment team determined that the monotonically convergent trend and conservative acceptance criterion (RH < 1) provide sufficient confidence for the intended regulatory use. The overall credibility body of evidence supports an Accepted decision at Medium assurance level for MRL 2.",
